              <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-5 text-left">
                <h4 class="text-uppercase">let me <br>Tell You<br>About myself</h4>
                <p class"text-about-section">Initially, I was first inspired to create a career services blog because being a first generation college student was really tough. </p> 
                  <p>During my senior year of highschool, I felt lost. In the sense where I had no one to really get advise from. I didn't quite know what I wanted to study at college. But since I was a child, my parents 'gave' me options of what I should become in the future. I had frequent meetings with my advisor about college, and I felt like I was running out of time. Then I just decided to major in Business Administration.</p>
                  <p>Fast forward to 2 years later, I then went on to change my major 3 more times. <i>My goal </i>in creating this blog is to inform everyone to choose their own career path. Forget what everyone else thinks.</p>
              </div>
                <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-7 text-center text-md-start">
